{"id":26,"ayahs":[{"number":170,"arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱتَّبِعُوا۟ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ قَالُوا۟ بَلْ نَتَّبِعُ مَآ أَلْفَيْنَا عَلَيْهِ ءَابَآءَنَآ ۗ أَوَلَوْ كَانَ ءَابَآؤُهُمْ لَا يَعْقِلُونَ شَيْـًۭٔا وَلَا يَهْتَدُونَ","translation":"But when they are told, \"Follow what God has bestowed from on high,\" some answer, \"Nay, we shall follow [only] that which we found our forefathers believing in and doing.\" Why, even if their forefathers did not use their reason at all, and were devoid of all guidance?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/177.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":82845,"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82846,"position":2,"arabic":"قِيلَ","translation":"বলা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82847,"position":3,"arabic":"لَهُمُ","translation":"তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82848,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱتَّبِعُوا۟","translation":"''তোমরা অনুসরণ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82849,"position":5,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82850,"position":6,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82851,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ''","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82852,"position":8,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82853,"position":9,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"''বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82854,"position":10,"arabic":"نَتَّبِعُ","translation":"আমরা অনুসরণ করব","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82855,"position":11,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"তা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82856,"position":12,"arabic":"أَلْفَيْنَا","translation":"আমরা পেয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82857,"position":13,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"যার উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82858,"position":14,"arabic":"ءَابَآءَنَآ ۗ","translation":"আমাদের বাপ-দাদাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82860,"position":15,"arabic":"أَوَلَوْ","translation":"যদিও কি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82861,"position":16,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"ছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82862,"position":17,"arabic":"ءَابَآؤُهُمْ","translation":"বাপ দাদারা তাদের (এমন যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82863,"position":18,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82864,"position":19,"arabic":"يَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"তারা বুঝতো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82865,"position":20,"arabic":"شَيْـًۭٔا","translation":"কিছুই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82866,"position":21,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82867,"position":22,"arabic":"يَهْتَدُونَ","translation":"তারা সৎ পথে চলত","audioUrl":"wbw/002_170_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82868,"position":23,"arabic":"١٧٠","translation":"(১৭০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":171,"arabic":"وَمَثَلُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ كَمَثَلِ ٱلَّذِى يَنْعِقُ بِمَا لَا يَسْمَعُ إِلَّا دُعَآءًۭ وَنِدَآءًۭ ۚ صُمٌّۢ بُكْمٌ عُمْىٌۭ فَهُمْ لَا يَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"And so, the parable of those who re bent on denying the truth is that of the beast which hears the shepherd's cry, and hears in it nothing but the sound of a voice and a call. Deaf are they, and dumb, and blind: for they do not use their reason.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/178.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":82904,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَثَلُ","translation":"এবং উপমা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82905,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82906,"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82907,"position":4,"arabic":"كَمَثَلِ","translation":"এরূপ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82908,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"(এক রাখাল) যে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82909,"position":6,"arabic":"يَنْعِقُ","translation":"(চিৎকার করে)ডাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82910,"position":7,"arabic":"بِمَا","translation":"ঐ বিষয় যা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82911,"position":8,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82912,"position":9,"arabic":"يَسْمَعُ","translation":"শুনে (তার পশু)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82913,"position":10,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82914,"position":11,"arabic":"دُعَآءًۭ","translation":"হাঁকডাক","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82915,"position":12,"arabic":"وَنِدَآءًۭ ۚ","translation":"ও আওয়াজ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82917,"position":13,"arabic":"صُمٌّۢ","translation":"বধির","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82918,"position":14,"arabic":"بُكْمٌ","translation":"বোবা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82919,"position":15,"arabic":"عُمْىٌۭ","translation":"অন্ধ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82920,"position":16,"arabic":"فَهُمْ","translation":"তারা তাই (কোনো কথাই)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82921,"position":17,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82922,"position":18,"arabic":"يَعْقِلُونَ","translation":"বুঝতে পারে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_171_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82923,"position":19,"arabic":"١٧١","translation":"(১৭১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":172,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ كُلُوا۟ مِن طَيِّبَٰتِ مَا رَزَقْنَٰكُمْ وَٱشْكُرُوا۟ لِلَّهِ إِن كُنتُمْ إِيَّاهُ تَعْبُدُونَ","translation":"O you who have attained to faith! Partake of the good things which We have provided for you as sustenance, and render thanks unto God, if it is [truly] Him that you worship.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/179.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":83060,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83061,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83062,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83063,"position":4,"arabic":"كُلُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা খাও","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83064,"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83065,"position":6,"arabic":"طَيِّبَـٰتِ","translation":"পবিত্র জিনিসগুলো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83066,"position":7,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83067,"position":8,"arabic":"رَزَقْنَـٰكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের জীবিকা দিয়েছি আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83068,"position":9,"arabic":"وَٱشْكُرُوا۟","translation":"ও তোমরা কৃতজ্ঞতা প্রকাশ করো","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83069,"position":10,"arabic":"لِلَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83070,"position":11,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83071,"position":12,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা হও (এমন যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83072,"position":13,"arabic":"إِيَّاهُ","translation":"শুধু তাকেই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83073,"position":14,"arabic":"تَعْبُدُونَ","translation":"তোমরা ইবাদাত কর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_172_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83074,"position":15,"arabic":"١٧٢","translation":"(১৭২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":173,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا حَرَّمَ عَلَيْكُمُ ٱلْمَيْتَةَ وَٱلدَّمَ وَلَحْمَ ٱلْخِنزِيرِ وَمَآ أُهِلَّ بِهِۦ لِغَيْرِ ٱللَّهِ ۖ فَمَنِ ٱضْطُرَّ غَيْرَ بَاغٍۢ وَلَا عَادٍۢ فَلَآ إِثْمَ عَلَيْهِ ۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ غَفُورٌۭ رَّحِيمٌ","translation":"He has forbidden to you only carrion, and blood, and the flesh of swine, and that over which any name other than God's has been invoked; but if one is driven by necessity - neither coveting it nor exceeding his immediate need -no sin shall be upon him: for, behold, God is much-forgiving, a dispenser of grace.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/180.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":83116,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","translation":"মূলতঃ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_173_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83117,"position":2,"arabic":"حَرَّمَ","translation":"(হারাম) করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_173_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83118,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمُ","translation":"তোমাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_173_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83119,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَيْتَةَ","translation":"মৃত (জন্তু)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_173_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83120,"position":5,"ara