"id":83137,"position":21,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ ۚ","translation":"তার উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_173_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83139,"position":22,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_173_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83140,"position":23,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_173_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83141,"position":24,"arabic":"غَفُورٌۭ","translation":"বড় ক্ষমাশীল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_173_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83142,"position":25,"arabic":"رَّحِيمٌ","translation":"পরম দয়ালু","audioUrl":"wbw/002_173_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83143,"position":26,"arabic":"١٧٣","translation":"(১৭৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":174,"arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ يَكْتُمُونَ مَآ أَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ مِنَ ٱلْكِتَٰبِ وَيَشْتَرُونَ بِهِۦ ثَمَنًۭا قَلِيلًا ۙ أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ مَا يَأْكُلُونَ فِى بُطُونِهِمْ إِلَّا ٱلنَّارَ وَلَا يُكَلِّمُهُمُ ٱللَّهُ يَوْمَ ٱلْقِيَٰمَةِ وَلَا يُزَكِّيهِمْ وَلَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌ","translation":"VERILY, as for those who suppress aught of the revelation which God has bestowed from on high, and barter it away for a trifling gain - they but fill their bellies with fire. And God will not speak unto them on the Day of Resurrection, nor will He cleanse them [of their sins]; and grievous suffering awaits them.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/181.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":83238,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_174_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83239,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_174_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83240,"position":3,"arabic":"يَكْتُمُونَ","translation":"গোপন করে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_174_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83241,"position":4,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_174_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":83242,"position":5,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ ক